content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21ยง 1.19 - Temporary permit or registration revoked by denial of application

State Regulations

An order of the commission denying an application for a
license or registration shall, unless otherwise stated, forthwith revoke and
annul any temporary permit or temporary registration issued pending final
action on the application for a license or registration. Notes
